---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="min-h-screen">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="relative text-primary-foreground py-20 px-4 bg-[#f6f6f6]">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="text-center animate-fade-in">
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333]"
          >
            About Sound Vision 360 Electronics
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-[#333333]">
            Crafting Immersive Environments Since 2005
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Mission Section */}
    <section class="py-16 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 animate-fade-in">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333]">
              Our Mission
            </h2>
            <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
              For nearly two decades, Sound Vision 360 Electronics has been at
              the forefront of integrating cutting-edge technology to transform
              how our clients live, work, and connect. Founded in 2005, our name
              reflects our core philosophy: to deliver a complete, 360-degree
              sensory experience through superior sound, visionary technology,
              and seamless electronic solutions.
              <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
                We began with a simple mission: to bridge the gap between
                complex technology and everyday usability. Today, we are a
                trusted partner for homeowners and businesses alike, designing
                and installing sophisticated systems that are as intuitive as
                they are powerful.
              </p>
            </p>
            </div>
            <div class="animate-fade-in h-[450px]">
              <img
                src="/miguelito.jpg"
                alt="Sistema de seguridad profesional"
                class="h-full rounded-lg shadow-2xl w-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
              />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Values Section */}
      <section class="py-16 container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <h2  class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333]">Our Comprehensive Solutions</h2>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We provide a holistic suite of services tailored to meet the evolving
          demands of the modern world:
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Integrated Technologies & AV Solutions: From boardrooms to living
          rooms, we design and implement comprehensive audio-video systems that
          enhance communication, entertainment, and productivity for both
          residential and commercial clients.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Residential Entertainment & Connectivity: We specialize in creating
          breathtaking Home Theaters and Media Rooms, along with whole-home
          Audio Distribution and robust Home Networks, ensuring your
          entertainment and connectivity are flawless in every corner of your
          home.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Commercial & Residential Security: Your safety and control are
          paramount. We offer state-of-the-art Security Camera Systems, Access
          Control solutions, and specialized Sound Masking technology to ensure
          privacy and security in any environment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Dynamic Digital Displays: We bring your message to life with
          professional LED Screen installation for impactful advertising,
          information displays, and event production.
        </p>
        <h3  class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333]">The Sound Vision 360 Difference</h3>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          What sets us apart is our unwavering commitment to quality,
          innovation, and client satisfaction. We don't just install equipment;
          we engineer experiences. Our team stays ahead of the technological
          curve, ensuring that every solution we deliver is built to last and
          designed to inspire.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#333333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Thank you for considering Sound Vision 360 Electronics. We look
          forward to the opportunity to bring vision to your sound, and sound to
          your vision.
        </p>
        <h4  class="text-xl md:text-center  font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333]">
          Welcome to a complete sensory experience. Welcome to Sound Vision 360.
        </h4>
      </section>
    </section>
  </div></Layout
>
